g.text: Using images and text headings to create a guided pathfor the eyes to follow was a vital part of this project. Even with a quick glance lasting millisecond, the path is well established. The viewer does not get lost or overwhelmed.Again, to reduce effort on the viewers side, two-columned text has been used 95% of the time as it maintains continuous flow of subject, and as opposed to single column, the eyes dont have to travel huge distances for each new line.
